    <h2 class="heading">Using colour</h2>

    <p>Pulsar uses a standardised colour palette which incorporates the colours defined in Jaduâ€™s styleguide.</p>


    <p>Particular care should be taken to ensure that any colours that interact with each other meet the <a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20/visual-audio-contrast-contrast.html">WCAG AA ratio for visual contrast</a> (4.5:1), which is especially important given that our main typeface (Proxima Nova) is rather thin.</p>

    <p>Colours variables are defined in the <code>_palette.base.scss</code> file and can be used anywhere.</p>


